  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Searing light temporarily radiates from your eyes and mouth. For the duration, you shed bright light in a 10-foot-radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet, and at the end of each of your turns, each creature within 10 feet of you takes <strong>radiant damage</strong> equal to your proficiency bonus.</p>\n<p>Until the transformation ends, once on each of your turns, you can deal extra <strong>radiant damage</strong> to one target when you deal damage to it with an attack or a spell. The extra damage equals your proficiency bonus.</p>",
